task.summary: Refactored nav drawer so that it uses the CreditCardHolder insted of a hacked in included xml
New fancy credit card backgrounds usind shapes and low sized drawables
New dialogFragment built to select a credit card from the nav drawer
AddCreditCard activity updated with new creditcard background selector and previewer!

Many bugfixes: - Camera FileProvider permission fix on pre-lolipop devices - icon_back_material.xml vector added, not found on pre-lolipop devices - LauncherActivity changed from AppCompatActivity to normal Activity due to exception. - Misc fixes..
ExpenseDetailActivity revamp: - Added Category and Type - Added Delete and Edit and Edit Image buttons - Implemented Delete action - Added Toolbar and BackIcon in toolbar
New CreditCard and CreditPeriod not found exceptions
AddCreditCard now adds an initial CreditPeriod according to ClosingDay and ExpenseLimit
LineChartFragment now loads ACTIVE_CC_ID's current CreditPeriod
Removed HomeActivity hack when deleting expenses from inside an ExpenseViewHolder, implemented an OnDeletedListener
CreditPeriod, Expsnse: Added constructors without id
NavDrawer now loads default ACTIVE_CC_ID, also improved other stuff
Refactored out an OverviewFragment from the contents of HomeActivity, leaving HomeActivity with a simple reusable DrawerLayout!
Implemented onActivityResult() when user deletes an expense inside the expenseDetails activity. ExpenseAdapter / Holder housekeeping
CreateExpense refactored to CreateAndEditExpense, other changes
New DateUtils, refactored out Date-related string methods into it. Also removed the Edit and Delete buttons in the ExpenseDetailActivity, replaced with Toolbar Menu icons!
Navigation drawer links working! Navigation Drawer header now refreshes fragments when changing credit card! Changed Overview Expenses ViewHolder XML
Fix: When editing an expense, old date was getting overwritten with date of edit
Close navDrawer when selecting an item, after refreshing the home fragment.
